Patch Set 15: Code-Review-1

(1 comment)

It looks good overall but I think it should be disabled by default. Cloud admins should enable it explicitly as their current configuration files do not have this options and after upgrade from previous version of Glance this profiling feature will be enabled by default.

Patch Set 15:

HI Georgy, this profiling functionality will be involved by glance only if it is enabled + trigged, so even the option equals True,  client needs to send special headers that contains signed by HMAC trace_info, in such case profiling will be trigged (for details, ref http://paste.openstack.org/show/85722/ ). So the default option will change anything for existing deployment.
